## Conditions.ConditionTokens.parseConditionSetToken() method

Parses a [condition set token](./ts-res.conditionsettoken.md) and validates it against the qualifiers present in the supplied [qualifier collector](./ts-res.qualifiers.ireadonlyqualifiercollector.md)<!-- -->.
